lead_paragraph: Jon Lester had a no-hitter in the back of his mind. He wound up giving up five hits, but gave the Chicago Cubs what they needed most.

headline.print_headline: Rizzo Homers Again, Lester Tough as Cubs Beat Reds 8-1
